.Dd $Mdocdate: April 28 2018 $
.Dt ACPIHVE 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm acpihve
.Nd Hyper-V entropy
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "acpihve* at acpi?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Hyper-V hosts make entropy available to guests in the OEM0 ACPI table.
The
.Nm
driver feeds this entropy into the kernel's entropy pool.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr acpi 4 ,
.Xr enqueue_randomness 9
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 6.1 .
